---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="About Mariana Costa, data engineer and open-source contributor.">
  <div class="about-page">
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-avatar">
        <img src="/img/profile.jpg" alt="Mariana Costa" width="88" height="88" />
      </div>
      <h1>Mariana Costa</h1>
      <p class="about-bio">
        I have a B.E. in Production Engineering from the Federal University of Rio Grande do Norte (Brazil)
        and I'm currently working with data analysis. I'm enthusiastic about data culture and problem-solving,
        and my favorite card is "conquering 24 territories of my choice" in War.
      </p>
      <div class="about-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/mrncstt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrncstt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>What I do</h2>
      <p>
        I work with data pipelines to the finance world. Most of my day-to-day involves
        PySpark/Git/Databricks jobs/Terraform, but I'm also drawn to the edges: contributing
        to open-source projects, building visualizations, and writing about what I learn along the way.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>This blog</h2>
      <p>
        A mix of technical, short TIL notes, and the occasional post (misc of topics).
        I write in English, Spanish and Portuguese depending on the topic and audience.
        Everything here reflects things I've actually built, broken, or tried to figure out.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
      <p>
        You can find my code on <a href="https://github.com/mrncstt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        and connect with me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrncstt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
        I'm also occasionally active in data engineering communities and open-source projects.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="about-disclaimer">
      All opinions are my own.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
